## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Runtime** | Node.js |
| **Framework** | Express.js |
| **Database** | <%= database.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + database.slice(1) %> |
| **ORM / ODM** | <%= orm !== 'none' ? orm.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + orm.slice(1) : 'Native Drivers' %> |
| **Package Manager** | <%= packageManager %> |

